post_title: Bringing a few cards to the National for a cash sale (Not set up as a dealer)
post_content:
Hello.  I am bringing a few T206's plus other graded cards to the National for a cash sale if anyone is interested.  We could meet in the food court area (if they have one).  Please let me know if interested and I can give you my phone number to meet up.
Please excuse the poor scans.  It seems only PSA slabs scan decently.

Bender - $550.00
Young - $850.00

Thanks,
Bob
